text:
God bless you .. Youssef Sharif mourns Haitham Ahmed Zaki
07 Nov 2019, 05:21 by Mohamed Badran
Mohammad Badran mourned the artist Yousef Al-Sharif, his colleague Haitham Ahmed Zaki, who passed away this morning at the age of 35 years. The artist Haitham Ahmed Zaki had left in the early hours of Thursday morning, at the age of 35 years, due to a sharp decline in blood circulation, but the prosecution decided to dissect the body to confirm the cause of death.
